                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">钱穆在新解中对孔子推崇备至，以圣心注解，盖因孔子学说经过上个世纪轰轰烈烈的新文化运动，文革运动之后，已是面目全非。论语这本书确实伟大，如此读过一遍，不敢说读过，读论语，需用此生此身读方能言读过。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="798128477">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-798128477" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-798128477" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="798128477">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/whoselee/">鳨</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-02-29</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">良师益友。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="705310870">
